# Radix Ratz
![image|500x500](upload://qaFGgDR2J9LG6BWkZP3LQiAIBky.jpeg)
>The Radix Ratz live deep in the sewers of London, they sneaked out of the Radix Labs following Mainnet launch in 2021 and they will soon be ready for new homes. This is you chance to be part of the Radix team in one of the first NFT projects launching on this ground breaking technology. There will only be 10 000 Ratz minted, and our token is the RATZ token. **Price of each NFT**: 50 XRD **Links**: * [Website](https://www.radixratz.com) **Social:** * [Twitter](https://twitter.com/RadixRatz) * [Telegram](https://t.me/Radixratz)
